values:
i felt like it was time for a change.

new lj name: Rachel_Hatechel

today is january 21. 
today is joe curry's birthday.
joe lives in texas, so i don't get to see joe anymore.
a couple things you should know about this not so average joe:
he can always make me laugh about anything. he is easily the funniest guy i know. 
he's loveable like a teddy bear. i mean have you ever met someone that didn't love joe?
he's caring and sweet, he makes the best presents ever.
joe is the defination of good time. 
he has strong opinions and reasons to back them up.
most importantly, he's irreplacable.
there will always be a spot in my heart for this little joe bear.
i love my baby gurl joe. i hope you have a great birthday/year/life/hahaha.

i remember this one time. joe and i dressed up like prostitutes and shot up in a dirty alley. then we drank fortys and broke bottles all night long. i don't remember much from that night but i know we woke up on a playground and watched the sun-rise. we swang on swings until his mom picked us up and took us to get our haircut. man that was the day joe got his mohawk, that was also the day he contracted aids from a dirty needle. i'll never forget that day and i'm sure he never will either. good times. 

Rachel

when i was a kid, i thought i knew every bump in the road.

Rachel

i just got back from dallas, now i'm going to virginia.

Rachel

today was the last day of enjoying my family.
chris and i just had our first all out fight again.

it ended when he called me a trashy whore and walked out.

Rachel

i'm starting to think blockbuster is out to garnish all my wages. late fees...
i think last night i broke my vcr, along with the tape inside, which happens to be a blockbuster tape..

my throat hurts so much, it makes me eyes water.

rachel

who has been living in my body the past couple weeks?

or is the question

how did i get inside this body?

Rachel
all hitting matthew and alvaro did was prove you do not even care enough about amanda to control your anger on her birthday.

today, december 14th is amanda's 19th birthday, for that, this entry is dedicated to her.
sentiments:
Another year has gone by, more boys and tears and fights (never between us).. It seems weird to say that we've been best friends since we were 12. We've crossed so many bridges together, our most recent college and moving out. I wouldn't have it any other way. I wouldn't change any aspect of our friendship. You mean more to me than any other person in this world and I would sarcafice anything to make you happy. I would drop anything and everything to help you out or be by your side and you best believe i would raise hell on your behalf. you are my perfect friend, no one else could ever wish to take your place or be half the friend you are to me. I don't know where we will be next year at this time, i'd like to think we will still be hanging out, regardless of where we are, i will love you more than i love you today.

It all began in 6th: i don't remember the exact day i met amanda. i do remember the goldfish at lunchtime, and sitting with emil and aaron. i remember created a stupid language so we could say they were stupid and weird. they watched our friendship begin. it's weird to think they had no idea what they were watching.

things i love about AMANDA:
*she laughs that i steal her pens and pencils.
*she grades my papers
*she wakes up at 5:20 in the morning to watch the sunrise with me.
*she puts up with my grumpy moods and tears.
*she always puts a smile on my face.
*she makes the best faces, like winks, etc.
*she can make me laugh under the most dire conditions.
*she puts her arm around me shoulders and helps me walk when i feel like it's too hard.
*she accompanies me on missions or errands.
*she understands me without saying a word.
*she goes along with every joke without missing a beat.
*i can predict when she will laugh. i always want to show her things to see her laugh.
*her laugh is contagious. 
*she carefully picks the things she stands up for.
*she still surprises me.
*she wakes me up in the middle of night so i can study.
*she has the best sense of humor.
*she's sensitive and caring.
*she can get along with anyone.
*she's as tough as they come.
*she lies and gets children's admission.
*she's a fat enabler.
*she knows how to shake her butt.
*she doesn't cave to peer pressure.
*she likes my pictures, even though they are shit.
i could go on forever.

Love,
Big Bro Rachie B

roomies just chatted decided:
beth has an idea, but doesn't want to do it at that particular time.
i know it's a bad idea, but try to convince everyone else it's a good idea and we should do it NOW.
amanda thinks its a bad idea but gives in to temptation.

Rachel

i branded my forehead today. it now says loser. i don't want people to meet me on false pretenses and think i am a cool kid.
i hope this isn't one of those things i regret in twenty years.

Rachel

today i slept 30 minutes through my first exam, that i never really found the time to study for. i feel asleep last night with the intentions of waking back up to study.. but my alarm either didn't go off or didn't wake me up. cut to the chase, i bombed my first exam that i was late for.

Rachel

ghost mice is tonight, and i have to work. arg. ARG. ARG.

ARG.

Rachel
JOE COMES HOME TOMORROW i'm so excited, i haven't seen him since my birthday and i miss him tremendously. he's the funniest guy i know. best friends 4 lyfe yall! Rachel

OMG, lightening bolt just got a shout-out on judge judy!

crappy daytime tv is awesome.

Rachel

MOTO | Ghost Mice | Hissing Choir | The Faeries Saturday, December 6. Banks Street Warehouse. 7PM. $5. An Idea Like No Other/Colossal Youth. AHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH i just ran and jumped on amanda on the couch to tell her. then we ran around screaming! Rachel locojoe87 (10:28:06 PM): man, if ghost mice play here, i swear....ill have to have a bag tied around my penis, because i will, i reapeat, i will pee

i lied. 
i admit that today.

yesterday, all the roomies went to see texas chainsaw massacre. i sat in between crystal and amanda. i laughed for a long time and i heard this girl in the row behind me say whats so funny. before the movie started, the screen went black for a couple minutes and amanda turned to us and says guys i can't see, she also tried to answer all the movie media questions about bone marrow and health, while i answered the movie ones. crystal screamed and grabbed at me and beth every couple minutes. she took phone calls during the movie. she is hilarious. beth hated the movie. we got ice cream after and she made best friends with everyone in the shop. 
we all have our quirks. i love us.

Rachel

Seth Rudesill made my morning.

Rachel
this is why i wear a bandana. Rachel

today amanda tried to bleach my hair. it wound up half orange, half black.. and not in a good way. steven let me borrow his bandana to hide this atrocity.
i'm decked out for halloween.
i've ridden my bike to sally's the past two days. first, i got hair dye remover (flop), then i got bleach (half ass job).. today they remembered my face, tomorrow they'll remember my name.

Rachel

this is what amanda looked like when she scouted out the area before deciding no one was around, that it was safe to steal crystal's purse. Rachel i knew amanda's room ate it. EDIT - OMG GUYS I JUST WENT IN AMANDA'S ROOM TO LOOK FOR THE KETCHUP AND I FOUND BETH'S LAPTOP AND MY OLD SCHOOLBAG WITH ALL MY BOOKS. WHAT SHOULD I DO.... I'M THINKING CALL CAMPUS POLICE... but i mean she is my friend.. friends don't steal friends backpacks.....

could you steal a purse from this face? so this morning i woke up and crystal says to me have u seen my purse?.. i replied i didn't even know you had a purse. then like an hour later amanda busted into my room and said CRYSTAL'S PURSE WAS STOLEN. -a reason to skip class - we skipped class to hang out with her and file the police report. poor crystal. i didn't even know she had a purse.. i wonder if things go missing that we don't even pay attention to.. like we only noticed beth's laptop, my books, and crystals purse.. but maybe more things have gone missing.. like today i couldn't find the ketchup.. no, that was in amanda's room. then last week.. i couldn't find this pot.. no, that was in amanda's room.. maybe all the lost stuff has been eaten by amanda's room..... Rachel
my underwear says hottie, cause thats what i am. Rachel
LOOK GUYS I DYED MY HAIR Rachel

i decided to fall in love with myself today. 

it's the only relationship whose bonds of trust will always hold strong.

the only relationship where i will never have to say a word. i'll just know.

i pledge to always be there when i'm hurt sick or upset.

i pledge to never leave my side.

i pledge to never get jealous of my interactions with other people.

i pledge to give myself my heart's desires.

Rachel

crystal and beth left for the weekend. i started doing dishes this morning. crystal left two really bad smelling things on the stove. one of them spilled all over the place including my clothes. i thought i was going to throw up. instead i just shrieked and ran away then threw my clothes on the ground. needless to say, i left the other one alone. then i went to take out the trash. omg. i don't know what crystal put in there. it smelled really bad also. i think the reason the trash smells so bad is she throws away organic stuff. amanda, beth, and i just throw away wrappers. i took the trash out in the rain. i'm glad it is out of the house.

Rachel

yesterday i went home to destrehan. mikey and i rode bikes by courtneys hallmark, the car wash, circle k.. it was like a ghost town. then we rode back on the golf course. i had a blast.

it was like back in the day when we 5 or 10.. i was waiting for my mom to say not to ride past rosedown. 

both our moms did say something about wearing dark colors.

i forgot how bad the mosquitoes are there. ouch.

Rachel

don't be mad at me anymore.

Rachel

dear journal,
i have a class with the boy in blue and i had no idea! he said hi to me and i had no idea! after class i ran away because i didn't want him to think i wanted to be best friends.
<3 always,
Rachel

i found amanda's livejournal password and i logged on just to look around. i was so shocked. this is one of her private journals: dear journal, today paul said i was his girlfriend and he loved me. ahhhhhhhhh.. i can die happy. -Amanda i hope she doesn't get mad! Rachel

Beths computer got stolen. someone is coming in our apartment and stealing our stuff. we think we know who it is: this boy anthony that kinda follows beth around. amanda was being stupid, she wanted to sit him down the next time he came by and tell him we know he did it, and he better bring it back or we are going to file a police report. the only good thing that came out of this, is that we have a much better relationship with crystal. crystal is hilarious. i <3 my roommates.

recently i have realized that i am like a big brother to amanda. meaning that i purposely do things to her that are gross or mean. crystal said we are like sisters, and i said no i'm like her big brother and she laughed.

Rachel

dear boy in blue,
did i forget to mention i love you.
<3 rachel

i've been sick since last sunday. it seems to be getting worse and better at the same time. first it was just that my throat hurt. then it progressed to a runny nose. then stuffy up nose. then coughing. then, a gross voice. now most of that is gone. i just have drainage and occasional coughing. i have absolutely no entergy. i don't want to move at all. yesterday i woke up at 11:30 after sleeping the whole night., then i went to sleep at like 4-11. then 11:30-2. then 4-6. than 6:30-8. all the 1ish hour breaks was because i was studying, and then i would get so tired i would just go to sleep. everything is fuzzy. i can't think clearly because i have been so sleepy. i feel detached from my body, i keep looking down thinking whose arms are those? i have a lose of appetite. i feel a little better now.. maybe it's waning.

it looks like someone stole my backpack, my math book, psychology book, and graphing calculator.
i hope i am wrong, and that it turns up somewhere.

bye bye $300+ worth of stuff.

rachel

Rachel

i have a math test today. it is easy math that i learned a long time ago. i feel like an idiot because i waited until yesterday to look at the textbook and.. it appears i actually need to relearn this stuff. i have never needed help in school.. and i will not need/have help now. Rachel

i walked out of my math class just now. i feel guilty.

i hate myself.

i want to drive somewhere, but i don't have anywhere to go.

Rachel

this boy just called my cellphone and asked for alisha. i said he had the wrong number, and he said we could be like blind date and hook up. after i laughed for a long time, which apparently wasn't dissuading, he proceded to ask me questions (if i was a white girl, if i had a man, if i've ever dated a black guy/do i have black in me, etc.) and try and hook up.... 

he sounded like fernando. i miss him.

Rachel

today is kissifers birthday!
i <3 my big brother.
he crank called me last night, i think he was drunk.. but i'm glad he thought of me and i'm glad it wasn't mean.
i hope he is doing well. i hope now that neither of us live at home, we can grow together rather than apart. i hope that this year is better than his last. i love his charming face, it shines bright. 
Happy 21 Chris. now if we ever go to the beach again the bars won't turn you down and piss u off.

Love,
Rachel

in english, we are writing a paper analysing a magazine ad. yesterday, this guy in my class brought in an ad of a picture of a cigarette in a glass ashtray with smoke all over the place. he went on and on about how smoking is bad and disgusting. today, on my way skipping sociology, i saw him smoking a cigarette outside talking to some girl in the shade.

?!?

Rachel

tonight i conquered the world, by having a big bonfire of every single risk game ever created.
it burned bright.

*i hate RISK.

Rachel

quick to the point:
back in action.
amanda and i moved into our apartment. only one of our roommates showed up. her name is beth. she is nice. she use to fight forest fires, seriously. she got food poisoning.. or so we thought. apparently she had a virus. we got the virus from her. so for about 36ish hours we were puking and crawling around the apartment moaning. <-- aka the first to second day of school. it was gross... our boys were very sweet to us.

i have been laughing alot.

Rachel

sunburned and moved.
no internet for a couple days.

Rachel

yesterday was the second time i was threatened to be fired at work for dating.
keep in mind my last day is two days from now.

Rachel

about 5 days until i move out and i just got grounded, how does that work?

Rachel
